1. TRADING DISCLAIMER
   This software is provided for EDUCATIONAL and INFORMATIONAL purposes only.
   The software does NOT execute trades automatically and does NOT guarantee
   any profits or accuracy in trading signals.

2. RISK WARNING
   Cryptocurrency trading involves substantial risk of loss. Users should:

   - Only trade with money they can afford to lose
   - Always do their own research (DYOR)
   - Consider consulting a financial advisor
   - Use proper risk management techniques

3. NO LIABILITY FOR TRADING LOSSES
   The authors and contributors of this software shall NOT be liable for any
   trading losses, financial damages, or any other losses that may result
   from the use of this software or its trading signals.

4. DATA PRIVACY
   This software collects minimal user data for functionality purposes only.
   No financial credentials, API keys, or sensitive personal information
   is stored or transmitted by this software.

5. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
   This software relies on third-party APIs (CoinGecko, Binance) for market
   data. The availability and accuracy of these services are not guaranteed.

6. COMPLIANCE
   Users are responsible for ensuring their use of this software complies
